Proportion of variables containing missings or complete values

Source: R/miss-complete-x-pct-prop.R
miss-complete-var-prop.Rd

Calculate the proportion of variables that contain a single missing or complete values.

miss_var_prop(data)

complete_var_prop(data)

Arguments

data

a dataframe

Value

numeric the proportion of variables that contain missing or complete data

See also

miss_case_pct miss_case_prop miss_prop_summary() miss_case_summary miss_case_table miss_summary miss_var_pct miss_var_run miss_var_span miss_var_summary miss_var_table

Examples


miss_var_prop(riskfactors)
#> [1] 0.7058824
miss_var_prop(oceanbuoys)
#> [1] 0.375
complete_var_prop(riskfactors)
#> [1] 0.2941176
complete_var_prop(oceanbuoys)
#> [1] 0.625
